g, and criticism, solidifying its reputation as a respected and authoritative voice in the industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Print and Digital Presence' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Initially published as a print magazine, *The Comics Journal* has adapted to the digital age by expanding its online presence. The magazine maintains an active website, featuring additional content such as interviews, reviews, and articles that complement its print edition.{{Category Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

