VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A comprehensive cricket magazine delivering news, analysis, features, and interviews for enthusiasts of the sport.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket, a cricket magazine targeting cricket enthusiasts, provides comprehensive coverage of the sport''s latest news, analysis, features, and interviews.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Origins and Publication' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket magazine was launched in [YEAR]. It has since become a popular publication for cricket fans, offering unique insights and expert analysis on the sport.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Cricket Coverage' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine covers cricket matches, tournaments, and events from around the world, including international cricket, domestic tournaments, and various formats of the game, such as Test matches, One Day Internationals, and Twenty20 cricket.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Features and Analysis' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket magazine offers in-depth features and analysis pieces, shedding light on various aspects of the game, including player profiles, cricketing techniques, strategies, and the behind-the-scenes dynamics of cricket teams and organizations.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Exclusive Interviews' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'One of the highlights of All Out Cricket is its exclusive interviews with cricket players, coaches, and other key figures in the cricketing world. These interviews provide readers with insights into the thoughts, experiences, and perspectives of prominent cricket personalities.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Match Reports and Statistics' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine provides detailed match reports, capturing the highlights and key moments from important cricket matches. It also presents statistical analysis of player performances, team records, and other statistical aspects of cricket.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Event Coverage' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket covers major cricket events such as the ICC Cricket World Cup, Ashes series, and other significant tournaments. The magazine delivers comprehensive coverage, including previews, analysis, match reports, and post-event summaries.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Coaching and Training Tips' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket magazine offers coaching and training tips from expert coaches and players, helping aspiring cricketers improve their skills and knowledge of the game. These tips cover various aspects like batting, bowling, fielding, and fitness.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Photography and Illustrations' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine features striking photography and illustrations that capture the essence and visual appeal of cricket. These visuals enhance the reading experience and provide a visual narrative of cricketing events and moments.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Online Presence and Digital Content' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, All Out Cricket has a strong online presence. Its website provides additional cricket content, including articles, videos, interviews, and interactive features, making it a comprehensive resource for cricket enthusiasts.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Awards and Recognition' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'All Out Cricket magazine has gained recognition within the cricketing community. It has been appreciated for its comprehensive coverage and insightful content, contributing to its credibility and reputation.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- Alternative Ulster
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Alternative Ulster', N'alternative-ulster', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A pioneering music and arts publication from Northern Ireland showcasing alternative culture and promoting local talent during tumultuous times.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Alternative Ulster magazine was a prominent music and arts publication in Northern Ireland. Focusing on alternative culture, the magazine provided a platform for local artists and musicians during a challenging period in the region''s history.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Origins and Publication' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Alternative Ulster magazine was first published in 1979 by a group of dedicated individuals seeking to create an outlet for alternative voices within the local music and arts scene of Northern Ireland. Notably, the name of the magazine was inspired by the influential punk song "Alternative Ulster" by punk rock band Stiff Little Fingers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Content and Format' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine''s content covered a wide range of subjects, including music, art, film, and societal issues affecting Northern Ireland and beyond. Known for its independent and alternative perspective, Alternative Ulster sought to explore countercultural movements and promote underrepresented voices within the creative community.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Influence and Impact' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Alternative Ulster magazine made a significant impact on the alternative music and arts scene in Northern Ireland. During a time of political and social unrest, the magazine provided a platform for artists to express themselves and share their work with a wider audience. It played a crucial role in fostering a sense of community and creativity during challenging times.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Promotion of Local Talent' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'One of the magazine''s primary objectives was to showcase and support local talent. Alternative Ulster featured interviews, reviews, and profiles of emerging and established artists, musicians, and creatives from Northern Ireland. It provided a valuable platform for artists to gain exposure and connect with a dedicated audience.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Editorial Approach' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Alternative Ulster maintained an impartial and non-judgmental editorial approach, focusing on promoting the local music and arts scene rather than imposing opinions or ideologies onto its readership. The magazine aimed to reflect the diversity and vibrancy of the alternative culture in Northern Ireland.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Discontinuation' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'After a successful run, Alternative Ulster magazine ceased publication in [year]. The specific reasons for its discontinuation are not widely documented, but the magazine''s legacy as an important contributor to the alternative cultural landscape of Northern Ireland lives on.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

