VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A celebrated Pittsburgh publication showcasing the city''s lifestyle, culture, and local businesses, with a focus on arts, entertainment, and philanthropy.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine, originally known as "Pittsburgh Magazine," is a prominent monthly publication based in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### History' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine was founded in 1977 by Richard DeShantz and Christy DeSmith. Initially named "Pittsburgh Magazine," it aimed to provide comprehensive coverage of the Pittsburgh region, including lifestyle, culture, entertainment, and local businesses.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Content' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine covers a wide range of topics, including arts and culture, dining, fashion, health, home and design, local events, and philanthropy. The magazine features in-depth articles, interviews with notable figures, guides to local attractions, and recommendations for restaurants, shopping, and entertainment venues.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Regional Focus' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine maintains a strong focus on the Pittsburgh region, highlighting the unique aspects of the city and its surrounding communities. It aims to promote the local businesses, events, and initiatives that contribute to the vibrant cultural fabric of the area.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Awards and Recognition' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine has received numerous accolades over the years. It has been recognized by the Western Pennsylvania Society of Professional Journalists, the City and Regional Magazine Association, and the Press Club of Western Pennsylvania for its quality journalism, design, and overall excellence.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Expanded Platforms' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, WHIRL Magazine has embraced digital platforms to reach a wider audience. It maintains an online presence, featuring articles, event listings, and additional multimedia content to engage readers beyond the printed page.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Community Engagement' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'WHIRL Magazine actively participates in community initiatives and charitable endeavors in the Pittsburgh area. It sponsors and organizes events, fundraisers, and partnerships that support local organizations and causes, furthering its commitment to community engagement.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

