INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription An influential publication promoting sustainability and global solutions, inspiring readers to create positive change in the 21st century.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Worldchanging magazine, also known as "Worldchanging: A User''s Guide for the 21st Century," was a prominent publication focused on sustainability and global issues.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Origin and Mission' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Worldchanging magazine was founded in 2003 by Alex Steffen, a journalist and futurist. The magazine aimed to inform and inspire readers about solutions to pressing global challenges, including climate change, poverty, resource depletion, and social inequality.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Content and Features' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine featured articles and essays written by a diverse array of contributors, including experts, activists, and thought leaders. It covered a wide range of topics, including sustainable design, renewable energy, social entrepreneurship, urban planning, and environmental conservation.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Worldchanging magazine not only explored the problems facing the world but also highlighted innovative solutions and practices that could help create a more sustainable and equitable future. It showcased real-world projects, technologies, and initiatives that were making a positive difference in various fields.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Influence and Recognition' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Worldchanging magazine gained recognition for its comprehensive coverage of global issues and its emphasis on positive change. Its forward-thinking approach and solutions-oriented articles resonated with a broad readership interested in sustainability, design, and social impact.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine''s influence extended beyond its pages. It served as a platform to amplify the voices of environmentalists, activists, and innovators dedicated to making a positive impact. Worldchanging magazine fostered a sense of community and inspired individuals to take action and become agents of change in their own communities.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Evolution and Closure' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to the print magazine, Worldchanging expanded its digital presence with a website that complemented its mission and featured regularly updated content. The online platform offered a space for discussion, collaboration, and the sharing of ideas.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Regrettably, Worldchanging magazine faced financial challenges and had to suspend its operations in 2010. The closure of the magazine was met with sadness by its dedicated readership and the broader community interested in sustainable and global issues.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Despite its closure, Worldchanging magazine left a lasting impact. Its insightful articles, thought leadership, and innovative ideas continue to resonate with individuals and organizations striving to create a more sustainable and equitable world.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

