VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A diverse monthly manga anthology featuring international content and engaging with a vibrant community of manga enthusiasts.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine, also known as *Yen+*, is a monthly manga anthology publication that features a variety of manga series from different genres.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### History and Publication' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine was first published in 2008, and it has been released on a monthly basis ever since. The magazine is published by Yen Press, a publishing company specializing in manga and graphic novels.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Manga Anthology' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine serves as a platform for showcasing a diverse selection of manga series. The magazine features a combination of serialized manga, one-shots, and exclusive content from both established and up-and-coming manga artists.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Genre Diversity' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine aims to offer a wide range of genres to cater to different reader preferences. It covers various genres, including action, adventure, fantasy, romance, slice-of-life, and supernatural. This diverse lineup aims to provide readers with a variety of storytelling styles and themes.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### International Content' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine includes manga series from both Japanese and non-Japanese creators. It features popular manga titles from Japan, as well as original creations and adaptations from other countries. This variety of international content adds to the magazine''s appeal and showcases the global reach of manga as a medium.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Digital and Print Availability' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine is available in both digital and print formats. Readers have the option to purchase physical copies of the magazine or access it digitally through various platforms. This accessibility allows fans to enjoy the magazine in a format that suits their preferences and reading habits.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'### Community Engagement' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Yen Plus magazine fosters a sense of community among manga enthusiasts by providing opportunities for reader engagement. The magazine encourages reader feedback, hosts contests, and occasionally features letters and artwork submitted by fans. This connection with its audience contributes to the vibrant and interactive nature of the magazine.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

