tained such a large readership despite the advent of online TV guides.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Online Presence' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Teve Guía has an online presence that allows its readers to access the print content, as well as receive updated TV listings and news as soon as they are available online. Additionally, Teve Guía subscribers can access the digital version of the magazine for free. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine has several social media accounts that are regularly updated with information relating to its content, as well as outside news and celebrity features.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

