ing multiple Pulitzer Prizes for sports reporting.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Sporting News was widely read by sports fans, coaches, and executives, and was considered a must-read publication for anyone interested in sports.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Sporting News ceased publication as a print magazine in 2012, but continues to exist as a digital publication. While the magazine is no longer published in print, its legacy as one of the most influential sports publications in American history lives on.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Sporting News was instrumental in shaping the way that sports news and events are covered in the United States, and its reputation for in-depth reporting and analysis of sports news helped to create a new standard for sports journalism.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

