VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A monthly lifestyle magazine published in Belize, covering social issues, fashion, sports and current events, with an online presence.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Open Your Eyes (OYE) is a monthly lifestyle magazine published in Belize, Central America. The magazine focuses on topics such as social issues, entertainment, fashion, sports, and current events.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Open Your Eyes magazine was first published in 2002 as a television program guide but has since evolved into a full-fledged publication catering to a diverse readership. Each month''s issue features articles written by local and international writers who offer different viewpoints on a range of subjects.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine is especially popular among Belizean youth who appreciate its fresh take on current events and its up-to-date coverage of local fashion and lifestyle trends. The magazine also features regular interviews with local and international celebrities, musicians, and influencers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Open Your Eyes magazine is owned and operated by Great Belize Productions, a media company based in Belize that also operates several other media outlets, including radio and television stations. The magazine has won several awards for its high-quality content and design, including the 2009 Belize Tourism Board''s Media Award for Best Local Magazine.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print edition, Open Your Eyes magazine also maintains an active online presence through its website and social media channels. The magazine''s website provides its readers with daily news updates, photo galleries, and videos of featured articles.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Overall Open Your Eyes magazine has become an integral part of