VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A monthly magazine targeting maritime professionals in the navy, coast guard, and merchant marine, published by the US Naval Institute.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Operations is a monthly magazine published by the United States Naval Institute (USNI) since 1973. The magazine targets maritime professionals in the navy, coast guard, and merchant marine, as well as professionals in related fields such as academia, defense contractors, and government agencies.{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine aims to provide its readers with a comprehensive overview of naval and maritime developments and technologies, as well as to promote critical thinking and debate around issues facing the seas. Each issue of the magazine features articles written by experts on diverse topics such as strategy, tactics, force structure, logistics, shipbuilding, and innovation, among others.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Operations magazine is well-regarded within the naval and maritime community and is considered an authoritative source of information on contemporary naval issues. Since its inception, the magazine has won numerous awards within the industry for its high-quality content and design.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The United States Naval Institute, which publishes the magazine, is a non-profit organization based in Annapolis, Maryland, that aims to advance the understanding and appreciation of sea power and national defense. The Institute was founded in 1873 by a group of naval officers and remains to this day an important forum for the exchange of ideas and the promotion of professional development within the maritime community.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print edition, Operations magazine maintains an active online presence through its website and social media channels. The magazine''s website provides its readers with daily news updates, online discussion forums, and access to the full archive of past issues.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Overall, Operations magazine is an important and well-respected publication within the naval and maritime community, providing its readers with authoritative and insightful content on contemporary issues facing the seas.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

