 CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Today, Othello Quarterly is recognized as an important publication in the history of Shakespearean scholarship and literary criticism. The magazine''s legacy continues to inform and inspire new generations of Shakespearean scholars and enthusiasts.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

