VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A biannual men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine known for its contemporary and avant-garde style, featuring emerging and established talent from the fashion industry.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Introduction{{Image image:magazine-cover-not-available.png|Type=PrimaryArticleImage}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero is a biannual men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine that covers a range of topics, from fashion and culture to music and art. The magazine is known for its stylish and sophisticated aesthetic, as well as its focus on emerging and established talent.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## History' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero was founded in London in 2009 by Fabien Kruszelnicki, who had previously worked as a stylist and art director. Kruszelnicki aimed to create a magazine that challenged the norms of traditional men''s fashion publications, with a focus on contemporary and avant-garde styles.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Since its launch, Hero has become one of the leading men''s fashion publications in the world, and has won a number of awards for its editorial content and design.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero features a mix of fashion, art, and culture content, with a focus on emerging and established talent. The magazine profiles designers, artists, musicians, and other cultural figures, and showcases the latest trends in men''s fashion and style.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine has also been known to incorporate provocative and boundary-pushing content, including essays on gender and sexuality, and editorial shoots that explore unconventional aesthetics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Collaborations' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero has collaborated with a number of leading brands and artists in the fashion and creative industries. The magazine has worked with brands like Gucci, Calvin Klein, and Adidas, and has featured editorials and interviews with iconic figures like David Beckham, Raf Simons, and Jaden Smith.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero has also collaborated with leading photographers and artists, including Ryan McGinley, Collier Schorr, and Inez & Vinoodh.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Circulation' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Hero is distributed worldwide, with a strong presence in Europe, North America, and Asia. The magazine has a loyal and diverse following of fashion, art, and culture enthusiasts, and is often seen as a leading voice in men''s fashion and style.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## References' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "Hero Magazine." Fashion Model Directory. Accessed August 30, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "Hero Magazine - A New Era of Men''s Fashion." KALTBLUT Magazine. Accessed August 30, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "Future Hero." The Business of Fashion. Accessed August 30, 2021.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

