g content have inspired readers to explore the world in new and exciting ways.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, High Passage has also maintained a strong online presence, featuring digital content and an online store selling travel-related products and accessories.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## References' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "High Passage Magazine." High Passage. Accessed August 31, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "10 Best Travel Magazines in France." Travel Radar. Accessed August 31, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "High Passage, le magazine qui inspire le voyageur." L''Officiel Voyage. Accessed August 31, 2021.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

